              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "I am back with Wasp weekly updates! I will try to do them every week from now on, as a sort of accountability mechanism. This one covers last couple of weeks:\n- Added support for newest, production-ready version of Prisma.\n- Added support for .env file.\n- PostgreSQL can now be used during development.\n- Moved CI from Travis & Appveyor to Github Actions -> it is faster, simpler and free.\nPlan for this week:\n- Looking into automatic CHANGELOG generation -> still figuring out how to set it up. "
              },
              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "http://conventionalcommits.org",
                "text": "conventionalcommits.org"
              },
              {
